---
title: Cheesy Pulled Pork & Corn Quesadillas with Garlic Yoghurt
description: Pulled pork in quesadillas is a given so let’s not stray from a classic, but we can make it a little interesting with the corn. Instead of a charred corn salsa (which we still love) add it to the filling for a sweet pop in the saucy pork. Trust us, you’ll love it!
